{"tid":1945857,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[召喚棋靈王]鮑起靜留英陪患病女兒 爆粗鬧英政府廢","createTime":"2020-03-27T10:08:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T13:54:57.000Z","uid":80516,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"03743ec5c6037ad93319804100d7966415ae9586","tid":1945857,"uid":80516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T10:08:32.000Z","msg":"金像影后鮑起靜（鮑姐）的女兒居英國，每年鮑姐都會飛到當地探望女兒及孫仔。今年2月中鮑姐跟Twins完成網劇戲份拍攝後，隨即飛到英國探望愛女，惟當地武漢肺炎亦開始大規模爆發，感染人數不斷上升。<br />\n<br />\n身在英國的鮑姐亦不禁於社交網上鬧爆當地政府：「那麽多人崇拜的大英帝國！請你唔好咁廢啦！到一個點了！救救你的人民！」留言一出，即有大批圈中人關心鮑姐，又着她要好好保護自己，其間鮑姐回應朋友時，更爆粗說：「要你自生自滅呀！乜X政府！」<br />\n<br />\n有報道指鮑姐如此生氣的原因，是因其女兒個多星期前病倒，持續低燒多時，但仍被當地醫院拒絕入院，問到鮑姐此事是否屬實？她以短訊回覆《蘋果》記者：「無事，有心了，她感冒啫。」之不過未見契仔陳展鵬留言慰問鮑姐。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200326/2Y73TLM3QIJCK7PRSXPV7MP2QI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200326%2F2Y73TLM3QIJCK7PRSXPV7MP2QI%2F&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNnB8Xc4SSRTU1%2BC3UxNwN9M%3D&h=ff56eb61\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200326%2F2Y73TLM3QIJCK7PRSXPV7MP2QI%2F&h=a1912361\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200326/2Y73TLM3QIJCK7PRSXPV7MP2QI/</a><br />\n<br />\n記得安慰下鮑姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"583670b9de32ec2e5323caa40b4b43bef3a81787","tid":1945857,"uid":200280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T10:55:17.000Z","msg":"夠唔夠膽屌中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6e7394f3faf1050b989c080b81ed5336f6e4ec2","tid":1945857,"uid":114504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T11:06:24.000Z","msg":"立即移民返支那"},{"pid":"1eb7a0c1eea54e355157bf10ce31d749441001af","tid":1945857,"uid":130303,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T11:09: